community_listings.title: Rhizome Community
community_listings.description: Note: Rhizome.org community page is protected by Cloudflare. Automated scraping requires Playwright with browser support. This file contains placeholder data until the protection can be bypassed.

note: Site protected by Cloudflare. To enable real data: Install Playwright (pip install playwright) and chromium browser (playwright install chromium), then re-run the fetch_rhizome.py script.
